    <item>
      <title>民调结果低于预期，印度股市损失 3860 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/india-s-stock-futures-rise-as-investors-await-election-result</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度股市暴跌，市值蒸发 3860 亿美元，因为选举结果显示，总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的执政党在全国大选中难以赢得多数席位，而此前的出口民调显示，莫迪有望获得压倒性胜利，这一结果令人震惊。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/india-s-stock-futures-rise-as-investors-await-election-result</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 01:02:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
